Ideas for xhippo

* Look for the different players and generate xhippo.config
  automatically depending on what's available.
* Options menu and dialog
* Abstracted-out interface support (GTK, GNOME, ncurses, WINGs...)
* Music preference management ("I don't like this song *that* much...")
* "Copy the name of this song" (to selection)
* Sort without "the"
